Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1048,980)}Mesarthim Adamas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,雙角之深緋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.44,0:23:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Alnasl Minium
