Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:23:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,水精之白鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:23:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,980)}Sadalmelik Albus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,牛頭王之琥珀...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(910,980)}Cor Tauri Succinum
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,學長！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,又要再一次...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,曉古城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.77,0:24:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好 狄珊珀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.84,0:24:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,時間到了 蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.68,0:24:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啟動「薔薇」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.30,0:24:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 請你振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.52,0:24:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,學長！
